# get_irida_analysis_result
# get the analysis result for a completed analysis submission
# returns analysisType and output file links
#
# WARNING: this endpoint queries Galaxy synchronously. it can take 15-60 minutes
# to respond depending on Galaxy load. Do not use during busy periods.
#
# usage: get_irida_analysis_result ANALYSIS_ID
#
# example: get_irida_analysis_result 24718
